sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User
    participant RA as RA (Coordinator)
    participant CA as CA (Context)
    participant EA as EA (Execution)
    participant IA as IA (Integration)
    participant MA as MA (Monitoring)
    participant OA as OA (Optimization)
    participant VA as VA (Validation)

    U->>RA: Submit task
    RA->>CA: Request context package
    CA-->>RA: Context package
    RA->>EA: Execute task
    EA-->>RA: Execution result
    RA->>IA: Integrate result
    IA-->>RA: Integrated output

    RA->>VA: Validate output
    VA-->>RA: Validation failed (policy/rule)
    RA->>MA: Check runtime health
    MA-->>RA: Alert: high error rate

    alt Recoverable issue
        RA->>OA: Request optimization strategy
        OA-->>RA: Tuned parameters + fallback action
        RA->>EA: Retry execution (attempt #2)
        EA-->>RA: New execution result
        RA->>IA: Re-integrate
        IA-->>RA: Updated output
        RA->>VA: Re-validate
        VA-->>RA: Validation passed
        RA-->>U: Return verified result
    else Non-recoverable issue
        RA->>MA: Raise incident with trace bundle
        MA-->>RA: Incident created + severity
        RA-->>U: Escalated failure (manual intervention required)
    end

    opt Safety rollback path
        RA->>IA: Trigger rollback to last known good state
        IA-->>RA: Rollback completed
        RA->>MA: Publish rollback event
        MA-->>RA: Observability updated
    end